<item>
            <title>[LU-5382] New static analysis issues in 2.5.58-75-g8b2f9c0</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5382</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Found 2 new issues in the build 2.5.58-75-g8b2f9c0:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pointer may be dereferenced after it was positively checked for NULL&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre/utils/lustre_lfsck.c&lt;/tt&gt;: in &lt;em&gt;jt_lfsck_start&lt;/em&gt;, Pointer &apos;optarg&apos; checked for NULL at line 182 may be dereferenced at line 174. Also there are 7 similar errors on line(s) 174, 195, 229, 274.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pointer may be dereferenced after it was positively checked for NULL&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre/utils/lustre_lfsck.c&lt;/tt&gt;: in &lt;em&gt;jt_lfsck_start&lt;/em&gt;, Pointer &apos;str&apos; checked for NULL at line 182 may be dereferenced at line 237. Also there is one similar error on line 237.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


